      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_FamilyTree_SecretChild.png">2f7d0004:00000000:3ac7063bf74ed94d</T>
      <T n="text">0x6294A201<!--String: "Did your Sim just have a child with someone who's not their official partner? Oopsie! Well, you may now choose to blatantly <b><font color='#199C2C'>lie about the real identity of your child's other parent</font></b>!\n\nWhen the <b><font color='#199C2C'>child is born</font></b> a pop-up menu will allow you to pick who shall be declared as the other parent. If you choose to lie and pretend that your official partner is the biological parent, your child will be considered a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Secret Child</font></b>. They will be treated as if they were truly related to their false parent, even allowing access to the same <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dynasty</font></b>.\n\nBe careful though, there's always a chance the truth might come out one day, causing a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Scandal</font></b> and undoing those false connections."--></T>
    </U>
